704026f.title: Brooklyn: Downing Street - Quincy Street
704026f.text:
Downing Street, west side, at Guincy Street. the 4-story building
is Nos. 6-8 Downing Street; its right hand portion and the vacant lots ad-
ioining it, correspond to the course of the Clove Road, which was also known
as ''the old road to Bedford''. The frame houses in the background, front on
Grand Ave.
About 191O.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
